

Creating a chat message:
1.Add a form
2.Listen to the form submit
3.When form is submitted, save to firebase -> (firebase.push({...}))
3a.When form is submitted, prevent the default (event. preventDefault())
4.Reset the form (maybe even focus the text box)

Display chat message body
1. Create a div (or li) to contain data
2. when a child is added, then call a function
3. Use messsageBody from Firebase ti set the textContent


    var message = {
      messsageBody: "yo, yo";
      username: "avand"

    }

4. Use the messsageBody from Firebase to set the textContent

5. Append the div (or li) to a parent
